description:
Danny recaps this week's Southern Charm, which featured the men going on an RV trip that is leaving Craig and Austen on the brim. Meanwhile, Chelsea and Madison plot to start a business together, Cam interviews a nanny, and we meet Kathryn's boyfriend Joe. This episode also features a Disney detour & Pellegrino conspiracy theory.
